        "markdown": "## Observability & Correlation IDs\n\nUse **X-Request-ID** (correlation ID) to trace a request across Web → API → Lambda → SageMaker → S3.\nSee runbooks: `docs/runbooks/OBSERVABILITY_RUNBOOKS.md`"
