    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 15,
      "width": 24,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "### Logs Insights – correlation ID\n\n**Find all logs for one request (replace `<CORRELATION_ID>`):**\n```\nfields @timestamp, @message\n| filter @message like /<CORRELATION_ID>/\n| sort @timestamp asc\n```\n\n**Top 10 slow by duration (if logs have duration_ms):**\n```\nfields @timestamp, @message\n| parse @message /\"duration_ms\":(?<duration_ms>\\d+)/\n| filter ispresent(duration_ms)\n| sort duration_ms desc\n| limit 10\n```\n\n**S3 upload failures:**\n```\nfields @timestamp, @message\n| filter @message like /S3 upload failed/\n```\n\nUse log groups: Generation Lambda, API Gateway access logs, SageMaker endpoint (if configured)."
      }
    },
